name: ArcGis Projects
body:
### Welcome to ArcGIS Projects Page.
This repository is meant for beginners, developers and curious gentry who can take as well as provide ideas through this platform.

```
$ cd cybercop001/arcgisprojects
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Idea
I had imported some experiments I had performed using ArcGIS products, for instance, ArcGIS API for JavaScript, ArcGIS 10.1 desktop, ArcGIS online and others. Visitors are welcome to post their comments as well as suggestions. 

### Authors and Contributors
Primarily I am looking for the development part. It also includes other people contributions too and that will definitely be honored.
